{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":100,"mouthOpen":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1007_00_01","textHome":"嗯？诶？一定要和我说才行吗？@天才的时间很宝贵的，这次就算特别待遇哦。@我是里见灯花。在宇宙相关的领域相当有名，@还写了书哦。另外，家里是医疗相关的团体，@对人体也很了解。有什么想知道的尽管问吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"id":100700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":100700,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"id":100700}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":1,"mouthOpen":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1007_00_17","textHome":"了解宇宙会使人类进化哦？@某种意义上，就像逐渐解开阿卡西纪录一样。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.9,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":7.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1007_00_18","textHome":"在魔法少女的历和人类的进化当中，@牺牲如影随形哦。@所以了解宇宙也是需要牺牲的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":100700,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":100700,"motion":200}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":100700,"motion":100,"mouthOpen":0,"pos":1,"tear":0,"voice":"vo_char_1007_00_19","textHome":"465亿光年的彼岸，又近了一步！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.2,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":100700}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"id":100700}]}],"group_13":